{"tid":1318621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好失焦！！","createTime":"2019-07-15T03:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T03:51:31.000Z","uid":126198,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f17947ece114653f4b6fed84e8a6f2fba7f2efbd","tid":1318621,"uid":126198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:37:00.000Z","msg":"琴晚睇緊live嗰陣真係嬲到仆街，但係之後見到頂車門嗰下又真係感動到喊咗出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇住克警棍棍毆落嚟，我想講我真係睇到好心痛，唔係叫大家唔好自由活動，但係希望義士真係小心自己安全，逼到啲犬出嚟ot已經好好架啦，適當時候真係要保存實力呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得閒嘅其實可以去做scout，起碼有增援或者封站都可以做定心理準備嘛，亦都可以減輕義士受傷嘅機會，其實都係幫緊前線（不過又要小心個個都去咗做scout點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n同埋我哋其實應該將矛頭對返住林鄭，唔好俾克警吉野家搶晒鏡，主角應該係hk vs 林鄭（港共）而唔係hk vs 克警，我哋目標應該係將港共政權暴行公諸於世，係背後攞克警做盾嘅人，應該係5大訴求，係真普選，係獨立調查會呀。<br />\n同埋其實自由活動同和理非要小心喺時間／地點上太接近，有人遊行冇預到俾犬打，冇預到見到警暴場面其實好正常，人哋唔想自由活動亦都無謂迫人，唔好俾藉口克警嚇退和理非，請記住和理非都有佢作為民意授權嘅作用，亦都係一個容易吸納多啲人嘅行動。<br />\n最後，都係果句，兄弟爬山，各有各做，互相幫助，不割席，不分化，不流血，不被捕，香港人加油！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ec5c0f5cd7a5eeda4b2309361a661ae6954b3a","tid":1318621,"uid":126198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:38:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09e750f4f441289cb41c88ca720cf58d3dfd124a","tid":1318621,"uid":126198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:38:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0938af855bc4eb6b37304e24b05aac76db34c1ad","tid":1318621,"uid":126198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:38:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52a8b8cc0cc7c376e9b94ca58c6a8e61ced38e02","tid":1318621,"uid":126198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b35324cc04e162d702074498cc6bc451aa2e099","tid":1318621,"uid":126198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:39:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46760281608c6f0e59c6086652b4ed4b1490f506","tid":1318621,"uid":126198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:39:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"882069def653694c6348c5aa286195be1576d4c5","tid":1318621,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:41:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8d5afc1b79634981dcb9f5b9a5c46d4c9c8266ee","tid":1318621,"uid":126198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:51:31.000Z","msg":"push"}]}